parameters: It's a well! Let's drink some water!
I need to pee, so maybe I should hold off for now...
Memerisu drew water and drank it!
Memerisu's health has been fully restored!
...Hmm, I think I might need to go to the bathroom now.

Memerisu now needs to pee! She needs to find a toilet or
she'll wet herself!
I also need to pee right now... Let's not drink any more.
Tina drew water and drank it!
It's cold and tasty... It's energizing
Tina's health has been fully restored!

Ah... I think I'm starting to feel the need to go to the
bathroom a little.

Tina now needs to pee! She needs to find a toilet or she'll
wet herself!
This is no place for kids! Get out of here!!

Eek, what's going on...!! They're really angry, it's scary,
so I better not get too close...
This is no place for kids! Get out of here!!

Memerisu-chan, if we cause a commotion during the day, we
won't be able to sneak in at night. Let's come back here
when it's dark.
I won't give it to you!

It's fine to rest at that inn, but it's better not to wander
around at night. There are crazies and prostitution rampant
out there.
Yeah, it seems better not to walk around at night.

Ladies only! Special free service event at the massage
parlor "Lymph"!

What's wrong, old man? You're muttering to yourself so
seriously and loud enough to be heard.
Hey, Memerisu! You shouldn't speak to him like that!!

Oh... young ladies... The truth is, my granddaughter has
been kidnapped by slave traders in the slums...

I've managed to find out that she's in this basement, but
there are guards, and this old man certainly can't retrieve
her...

Your granddaughter has been taken by slave traders...!?
That's terrible...!!

Are you ladies adventurers by any chance? If it's not too
much trouble, could you possibly rescue my granddaughter
from the slave traders...?

We must rescue her, or she'll be in danger... right,
Memerisu?

(Hmm... I want to help, but... this could be a really
dangerous request. I need to think carefully...)

Leave it to me! Memerisu will swoop in and rescue your
granddaughter in a flash!
Oh! Really!? Thank you... thank you...!!

It seems they hold a slave auction in the basement at
night... My granddaughter must be there... Please rescue her
before she is sold.

I see, so we just need to sneak in at night, right? Leave it
to me!

Sorry, old man... That request is just too dangerous. You
should ask a more professional adventurer or specialist.
It's alright... I apologize for asking too much...

The granddaughter should be up for auction at the slave
auction held in the basement here at night... Please, I beg
of you to help...

I feel like something unpleasant happened here... No, that
was a dream... It was just a dream, right?

This is the slums where even crying children fall silent!
Hyaha!!

Gehehe, this ain't a place for young ladies like you! It'd
be best for your own good to scram quickly!!
Mister... could you possibly be a good person?

Hey there, young ladies... You're quite young and cute. Do
you have any used toilets? If you do, I'll buy them at a
high price.
What the heck, you pervert!? Gross!!

No, no, don't get me wrong. I'm not that interested in
girls' pee.

It's just that there's a certain demand for girls' pee... I
buy it here and sell it at a higher price to those who like
it.

Hahaha, it's a trivial matter. Don't worry about it. Anyway,
if you bring me used toilets, I'll buy them.
You can now sell used toilets!

Oh! You have a used toilet with you! How about it, would you
let me buy your pee?
Oh! Fresh, warm pee...!! This looks delicious... *gulp*
You sold a used toilet for 800 jewels!
If you bring me a used toilet, I'll buy it at a high price!

Wow, there's a campfire! I happen to have some sweet
potatoes, maybe I'll make some baked sweet potatoes~

Yes, they're nicely baked~ Be careful not to burn yourself,
it's hot.

Yay~! They look fluffy and delicious! Tina-chan, let's eat
them together later

Oh, there's a campfire. If I had some sweet potatoes, I'd
want to make baked sweet potatoes.
